CEVIZ SOFTWARE LICENSE AGREEMENT
Version 1.0 — Effective 2026-04-29

Copyright (c) 2026 EONYAK OH. All rights reserved.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

1. DEFINITIONS

"Software" means the CEVIZ VS Code extension and all associated
backend scripts, documentation, and media files in this repository.

"License Key" means the unique alphanumeric key issued upon purchase
through the LemonSqueezy payment platform.

"Licensed User" means a natural person or legal entity that has
purchased a valid License Key.

"Trial Period" means the 14-day free evaluation period starting from
the first installation of the Software.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

2. TRIAL LICENSE

During the Trial Period, you may use the Software free of charge
subject to the following limitations:

  · Cloud AI calls: 50 per day
  · RSS feed subscriptions: 3 maximum
  · Workspaces: 1 maximum
  · Self-Development System (RAG): disabled
  · Voice input: disabled

Local AI (Ollama) is always available without restriction, including
after the Trial Period expires.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

3. PAID LICENSE PLANS

Upon purchasing a License Key, you are granted a non-exclusive,
non-transferable (except as provided in Section 6), perpetual license
to use the Software subject to the plan you purchased:

  Plan        | Price | Devices | Features
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Personal    | $49   | 1       | All v1.x features
  Pro         | $99   | 3       | All v1.x features
  Founder     | $149  | unlimited | All features, lifetime

"All v1.x features" means all features available in any v1.x release,
including features added after your purchase date.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

4. PERMITTED USES

Licensed Users may:
  a) Install and use the Software on the number of devices permitted
     by their plan.
  b) Use the Software for personal or commercial purposes.
  c) Receive all v1.x updates at no additional cost.
  d) Receive security patches for all supported versions at no cost.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

5. RESTRICTIONS

You may NOT:
  a) Redistribute, sublicense, sell, or transfer the Software or
     any License Key to third parties.
  b) Remove or alter any copyright, trademark, or license notices.
  c) Reverse-engineer the license verification mechanism.
  d) Share your License Key with others or use it on more devices
     than your plan permits.
  e) Use the Software to develop a competing product.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

6. LICENSE TRANSFER

You may transfer your License Key to a new device by deactivating it
on the current device first (Cloud tab → License → Transfer License).
The maximum number of simultaneously active devices is determined by
your plan (Section 3).

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

7. BRING YOUR OWN KEY (BYOK) POLICY

Cloud AI usage (Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini) requires the user
to supply their own API keys. CEVIZ does NOT charge for Cloud AI
usage; all API costs are billed directly by the respective providers
to the user. The License Fee covers only the CEVIZ software itself.

This policy ensures CEVIZ incurs zero marginal infrastructure cost
per user for Cloud AI, and the user retains full control over their
API spending.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

8. VERSION UPGRADE POLICY

  a) All v1.x releases (v1.0 through v1.x) are free for all
     Licensed Users, regardless of when they purchased.
  b) Major version upgrades (e.g., v1.x → v2.0) are optional
     paid upgrades. Existing Licensed Users receive a 50% discount.
  c) Security patches are provided free of charge to all versions
     under active support.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

9. REFUND POLICY

LemonSqueezy provides a 30-day money-back guarantee. To request a
refund, use the link in your purchase confirmation email or contact:
eonyakoh@gmail.com

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

10. OFFLINE USE

The Software may be used without internet connectivity for up to
14 days following the last successful online license verification.
After 14 days offline, an internet connection is required to
revalidate the license. Local AI (Ollama) remains functional
regardless of license verification status.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

11. DATA PRIVACY

The Software stores all user data (chat history, sessions, API keys,
license keys) locally on the user's device using VS Code's built-in
secure storage APIs. No user data is transmitted to CEVIZ servers.
The only external network calls made by the Software are:

  · License validation: api.lemonsqueezy.com
  · Cloud AI inference: api.anthropic.com or generativelanguage.googleapis.com
    (only when explicitly initiated by the user with their own API keys)
  · Backend update check: api.github.com/repos/eonyakoh/ceviz (weekly, opt-out via settings)

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

